    , "3D Printing in Healthcare: Innovations and Challenges"
    , "Smart Wearable Technologies for Remote Health Monitoring" , "AI-Powered Robotics in Precision Agriculture" ] }, {
    track: "AI for Agriculture" , note: "But not limited to…" , emoji: "🌾" , topics:
    [ "AI-Powered Precision Farming and Yield Prediction" , "Smart Pest and Disease Detection using Deep Learning"
